<p>After <a href="https://www.hashicorp.com/blog/terraform-collaboration-for-everyone">announcing our plans to bring HashiCorp Terraform collaboration features to everyone</a> last fall, we’re excited to introduce Terraform Cloud, a collaboration platform designed for all Terraform users. Terraform Cloud is a SaaS application that brings free collaboration features to individual users and teams with additional paid feature sets that provide team management, self-service infrastructure, and governance features. </p>

<p>After Beta testing the past few months, we’re excited to make the Remote State Management feature of Terraform Cloud generally available today. Other features to be made available later this year. Sign up for a Terraform Cloud account <a href="https://app.terraform.io/signup?utm_source=blog&utm_campaign=intro_tf_cloud_remote">here</a>! </p>

